  "text": "Mov va et al. [CITATION_1] also assessed PD-L1 expression by immunohistochemistry in 221 sarcomas and found that 57% expressed PD-L1 and that 54.8% were PD-1-positive. Significantly high of PD-L1 expression was seen in 19 of 60 l ms cases (32%), 12 of 16 chondrosarcoma cases (75%), 23 of 30 liposarcoma (lps) cases (77%), and 7 of 10 undifferentiated pleomorphic sarcoma (ups) cases (70%).",
